  <heading>SDIV</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Signed divide</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction divides the first signed source register value
by the second signed source register value, and writes the result
to the destination register. Dividing by zero writes the value zero to the destination register.
The condition flags are not affected.</para>
    </authored>
  </desc>
